>>“Multiple Lapses” – the graphic that was published along with the report, “Deploying NSG instead of Army was a mistake: experts” (Jan. 6, 2016), erroneously said the Headquarters of 9 Corps is in Yol, Shimla. Actually, it is outside Dharamshala.>>In “BCCI’s choice: enter the 21 century or fight to stay in the 19” (Between Wickets column, Sport, Jan. 6, 2016), there was a reference to Mumbai winning the Ranji Trophy 44 times. It should have been 40.